Repairing file(s) in cmdOS
.
	-How to get access to repair window?
	-Easy. Just type 'repair' in cmdOS or start 
	repair file in folder with cmdOS
.
Whats it does?	
.	
	This window can repair your kernel!
	Just open this window and select 1.KERNEL
	then select 1.REPAIR and start cmdOS.
	If you has blue screen about KERNEL_BROKEN
	repair must help
.
